OOC: Sorry Tucson, I didn't see that you had left the base to fly over.

As TUCSON arrived over the cave entrance he could immediately see it
as well as the PROTOHUMAN village nearby. He could see the statue not
too far off and the trail that led between the town and the cave and
the town and the mine entrance to the cave.

From the cave there was the sounds of dim laser fire, it came out
sounding somewhat like aggressive crickets as things went back and
forth!

There was a vague sense of PREDACON in the area but nothing specific,
perhaps they were in hiding, waiting for the nest moment of attack.

Deep behind a small hill, out of optical sight of TUCSON and the
others the PREDACONS were watching, crouching silently. The humans
that DINOBOT shot at had frozen, apparently in fight, that is until
they looked up at the hovering form of TUCSON in the air.

They smiled.

Covered by underbrush and foliage, they could see him, but they were,
at the moment, still hidden from view. However it was obvious they
were planning something,.

Suddenly there was a strange sort of 'THUD', then some sort of
explosion errupted and the cave and tunnel collapsed bringing tons of
rock towards RAT TRAP and PERCEPTOR as they struggled to get out of
the cave!

There was nothing from RODIMUS!

(TAG)

- Preston
